snippet.title: Quake: Abyss of Pandemonium - 01 Enter the Abyss - All Secrets - 1080p 60fps
snippet.description:
100% secrets playthrough of Quake's commercial addon Abyss of Pandemonium. Recorded in 1080p, 60fps, 105fov with no voiceovers or comments. The sourceport used is Quakespasm, a limit expanding quake port with full compatibility with old mods. You can get it at: http://quakespasm.sourceforge.net/

Addon link (it's now free): http://www.moddb.com/mods/abyss-of-pandemonium
